  "title": "Automation Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Servicing, installation, testing and troubleshooting of electrical and mechanical parts at clients' premises or workshop.</p>\n<p>Access control, able to work under minimal supervision.</p>\n<p>Experience in Security System is a plus.</p>\n<p>Job Requirement:</p>\n<p>Candidate must possess at least a NITEC, Professional Certificate in ( Electrical / Electronic / Mechanical) or equivalent.</p>\n<p>Must have basic Electrical/ Mechanical and Electronic background.</p>\n<p>Bilingual in English and Mandarin (in order to liaise with English and Mandarin speaking associates).</p>\n<p>Have a Class 3 or higher driving license.</p>\n<p>Have a CSOC is a plus.</p>\n<p>Able to start work immediately or short notice.</p>\n<p>Entry level candidates are welcome to apply.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WORKING AREA- SENOKO ROAD</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>TALENT LINK SOLUTION – (23C1962)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>PATRICK POH</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Reg No - R1107847</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WhatsApp- +6591089692</strong></p>",
